            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Rivian股價上漲5%，全年交付指引上調",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 電動車製造商Rivian Automotive（納斯達克：RIVN）股價週四上漲5%，此前該公司公佈了2026年第二季度的生產及交付數據，並上調了全年交付指引。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rivian在截至6月30日的季度內，於伊利諾伊州諾馬爾工廠共生產了1.2613萬輛車，並交付了1.2194萬輛。交付量超出公司此前預期的9,000至1.1萬輛區間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rivian表示，業績超預期主要得益於EDV及R1車型的環比強勁增長，以及R2車型交付的正式啟動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-af2f2b3c-a0af-39f7-9d44-e252d291df76-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基於第二季度的表現及下半年的業務展望，Rivian將2026年全年交付指引上調至6.5萬至7萬輛，高於此前的6.2萬至6.7萬輛區間。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次上調意味著指引中位數提升了3,500輛，較公司此前預測增加約5.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/rivian%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B25-%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF-133641238.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 21:50:37",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
